         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>Total of 4033 tiruviruttams. Āṟumukam is the refuge. The essence of Śiva. In the
               auspicious day when the Jovian year Cittāṟti, the month of Cittirai, the 20th day,
               Monday, the constellation of Cataiyam and the tenth [lunar day] fall together,
               Cāmiṉātaṉ son of Civakurunātamutaliyār who is in the great town of Putuvai fully
               finished copying the Periyapurāṇam that is copied for the of the property (contam)
               above mentioned. May Comacuntarēsparar be the refuge.</p>
         </div>
